\newlabel{tab:event-micro-threshold-robustness}{{A6}{4}{Alternate-threshold robustness for the event-micro benchmark. The same qualitative winner drift and recurrent deployed-suboptimality pattern persists when the fixed threshold is changed from $\tau = 0.55$ to $\tau = 0.50$}{table.A6}{}}
