\newlabel{tab:event-micro-hysteresis-robustness}{{A8}{5}{Second-interface robustness for the event-micro benchmark. Under a fixed hysteresis-threshold interface with $\delta = 0.05$, the same qualitative winner drift and deployed-suboptimality pattern remains visible, though the magnitudes are smaller than under the canonical fixed threshold}{table.A8}{}}
